-- Statoil Agrees to Sell 40% Alberta Oil Sands Stake to PTT for $2.3 Billion
-- B y   B e n   L i v e s e y
-- 2010-11-23T02:07:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-23/statoil-agrees-to-sell-40-alberta-oil-sands-stake-to-ptt-for-2-3-billion.html
Statoil ASA agreed to sell a 40
percent interest in its oil sands project in Alberta, Canada to
PTT Exploration and Production for $2.28 billion, it said in a
statement.   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
